Module tagtraum.japlscript.executor
Package com.tagtraum.japlscript.execution

Class ScriptExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tagtraum.japlscript.execution.ScriptExecutor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CocoaScriptExecutor, Osascript

    public abstract class ScriptExecutor
extends Object
    Abstract superclass for script executors. Concrete implementation may use different (native) mechanisms to actually run a given script, like the command line tool osascript or NSAppleScript.
    Author:
    Hendrik Schreiber
